  <summary>6/14/2006--Passed Senate without amendment.
Recognizes: (1) Ignacy Jan Paderewski's accomplishments as a musician, composer, statesman, and philanthropist and his invaluable efforts in forging close ties between Poland and the United States, on the 65th anniversary of his death; and (2) Poland as an ally and strong partner in the war against terrorism.</summary>
